OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FEconomic growth stalled in the rain in
OL,7,FApril.
OL,9,FThe headline is terrible news for
OL,10,FRishi Sunak in the middle of an
OL,11,Felection campaign, but then the
OL,12,Fheadline doesn't tell the whole story.
OL,14,FGrowth in the three months between
OL,15,FFebruary and April was up 0.7% on the
OL,16,Fprevious three months and there is
OL,17,Fplenty of evidence to support Sunak's
OL,18,Fclaim that a corner has been turned.
