OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FInflation has receded. Pay has been
OL,7,Frising faster than prices for eleven
OL,8,Fmonths and interest rates are forecast
OL,9,Fto start edging down in the months
OL,10,Fahead.
OL,12,FThere's every reason to be hopeful
OL,13,Fthat the worst is now behind us.
OL,15,FThe UK has been hit by a series of
OL,16,Feconomic shocks in recent years, but
OL,17,Four economic problems pre-date the
OL,18,Fpandemic, the invasion of Ukraine, and
OL,19,FBrexit.
