OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FThese are highly desirable aims, but
OL,7,Fthe question we should be asking is
OL,8,Fwhich party has a convincing plan to
OL,9,Fdeliver them?
OL,11,FWhich party has the policies that are
OL,12,Flikely to increase business investment
OL,13,F(which has been lethargic since
OL,14,FBrexit), public investment,
OL,15,Fproductivity and economic growth?
OL,17,FThere is more to life to GDP but
OL,18,Fgoodness it helps - not least if you
OL,19,Fwant the tax revenues to improve
OL,20,Ffunding for public services.
